{"tid":1081648,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"代表助斯諾登難民律師：香港充斥種族主義 排斥，迫害難民","createTime":"2019-03-28T11:55:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-28T16:43:48.000Z","uid":133680,"like":3,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"b52a2993d8eefd21732d4cf34c4ef004f2dda629","tid":1081648,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T11:55:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190326/59411128\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190326%2F59411128&d=pW%2BpET2SRZmQ0hv433X7AIjkqoP0ISDA%2F8fQ3RVu%2FF4%3D&h=f1ee33f9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190326%2F59411128&h=a8ad2903\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190326/59411128</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190325/large/1553523387_51e2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190325%2Flarge%2F1553523387_51e2.png&h=0eee8ff3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n港難民篩選制度欠透明公正 成功機會近乎零<br />\n<br />\n在香港收留斯諾登的3個難民家庭早前曾向港府申請酷刑聲請，全部被拒。其中獲加拿大批准難民身份的Vanessa在港生活近20年，<span style=\"color: red;\">她認為香港政府將申請庇護者當作香港的垃圾（rubbish in Hong Kong）。在香港的難民沒有工作、沒有金錢，沒有希望和未來，有如生活在地獄之中。</span> <br />\n協助她的<span style=\"color: red;\">大律師田光譽</span> （Robert Tibbo）向《蘋果》稱，<span style=\"color: red;\">加拿大的難民篩選制度遠較香港透明和公平，形容香港是「種族主義、歧視、排斥和迫害的世界」（a world of racism, discrimination, exclusion and persecution）。</span> <br />\n<br />\n田光譽向《蘋果》表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">Vanessa及其女兒在香港遭受歧視和邊緣化，她不被允許工作，亦沒有足夠的人道主義援助滿足其基本需求，其女兒更因膚色多次遭受種族歧視</span> 。田光譽對於加拿大的審批結果非常高興，形容自己7年來為斯諾登難民的權利和自由而戰，<span style=\"color: red;\">Vanessa及其女兒終於離開充滿歧視的香港，將在加拿大這包容的社會中，找到安全和自由。</span> <br />\n<br />\nVanessa的申請在香港被拒卻在加拿大獲批，田光譽認為，<span style=\"color: red;\">加拿大的難民篩選制度比香港更加透明和公平，與當地民主制度有關</span> 。田光譽指，<span style=\"color: red;\">在香港難民申請的成功機會低於0.5%，而加拿大的成功率則有50%。</span> 加拿大設有公開的聽證會，香港的審查卻完全不對公眾開放；加拿大移民官若認為申請可能不成功，將給予尋求庇護者補充證據的機會，香港則沒有這程序。<br />\n<br />\n田光譽批評，香港入境處人員缺乏這方面的訓練，在決定是否批准個案時，經常低估和忽視證據，形容他們對文化並不敏銳（lack of cultural sensitivity），亦對弱勢群體缺乏同情。田光譽指出，目前仍有5名曾收留斯諾登的難民在香港，加拿大當局仍未就其難民申請下決定，已要求加拿大當局盡快行動，將他們全部接到當地。"},{"pid":"7efae3b507ea9fbe268c664c2458095811077098","tid":1081648,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T11:59:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd7a1660f175b434c2185b4e2c775bc3daa5e09e","tid":1081648,"uid":156913,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T12:00:15.000Z","msg":"Right, so don't come here, go to Germany<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf11c335ab99a138737d9c4a6b5c019e03a8fea6","tid":1081648,"uid":33651,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T12:00:31.000Z","msg":"收你班難民就67啦<br />\n乜鳩都唔做淨係入侵人地屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcffa1a6d5bf179b8a80e1d006198ebf03ba366a","tid":1081648,"uid":33651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd7a1660f175b434c2185b4e2c775bc3daa5e09e","tid":1081648,"uid":156913,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T12:00:15.000Z","msg":"Right, so don't come here, go to Germany<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T12:00:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7b5b91468d0a7a1aa7ffc196c1f4575f234b57b","tid":1081648,"uid":39855,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T12:00:48.000Z","msg":"吊，加拿大有50%，我都做難民啦！"},{"pid":"153d499c845048abe5974fd5e0f0aa731390ef41","tid":1081648,"uid":9542,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T12:01:09.000Z","msg":"事實係唔怕認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{